text: Prague Skate was an international figure skating competition organized in Czechoslovakia from October 28 to November 1, 1992. Medals were awarded in the disciplines of men's singles, ladies' singles and pair skating. The event was organized as a test competition for the 1993 World Figure Skating Championships. ==Men== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Rank ! Name !
